			Company Description 
		


                Scio Diamond Technology Corp. engages in the development and production of crystal diamond materials. It intends to pursue development of its core diamond materials technologies and related intellectual property. The company was founded on September 17, 2009 and is headquartered in Greenville, SC.
            




