Scio Diamond







High Quality,
        Single-Crystal Diamonds
        Scio Diamond creates high quality, single-crystal, Type IIa diamonds for the jewelry market and industrial applications. The company employs a patent-protected chemical vapor deposition (CVD) process in a precisely controlled laboratory setting to produce diamonds.



 




Lab-Grown vs.Mined Diamonds
          Lab-grown diamonds are chemically, physically and optically identical to mined diamonds. Scio Diamond’s technology offers the flexibility to produce lab-grown diamonds in size, color and quality combinations that are rare in mined diamonds.
        


 




Diamonds for the Future
          Today’s industrial and gem applications are just the beginning.  The application of diamond and diamond films in areas like advanced electronics and water purification offer exceptional promise.
        


 





SEE THE FULL STORY





